Phishing Proof by IPHawk is a Phishing URL detection extension that uses Artificial Intelligence to detect URLs and website content designed to dupe you into giving away personal information, and block them.

Our advanced AI engine analyzes the website content and domain name details our generates a prediction on the authencity of the website.

It works in the background and takes intelligent decisions for you by proactively blocking all form fields on suspicious websites.
